quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Twaa, Siiyn, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa). Aya n’amajambo ari mugitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kandi n’igitabu cuzuye mwo ibintu vyose ngira kamaro kandi n’igitabu gisigura ibikenewe vyose biri mw’idini rya Isilaamu"
  27,2,Iyi Qur’aani n’uburongozi hamwe n’inkuru nziza ku bantu bayemera bimwe vy’ukuri
  27,3,Aribo bahagarika amasengesho nugutanga imperezwa zabo nabo bafise icizero c’umusi w’imperuka
  27,4,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batemera uwo musi w’imperuka twebwe twarasharije ibikorwa vyabo, kuri ivyo baguma batayataya"
  27,5,Abo nibo bazoronka ibihano bibi cane kandi abo nyene mw’ijuru nibo bazoronka uruhombo runiniya cane
  27,6,Mu vy’ukuri ni wewe wigishwa iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ivuye kuwufise ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagije
  27,7,"Igihe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yabwira umuryango wiwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye umukomezwa, ubu vuba ndabazanira inkuru zawo canke ndabazanira igishirira cawo caka kugira ngo mwote kuri uwo mukomezwa"
  27,8,"Mugihe yawushikira yaciye ahamagarwa ati:- wewe arahezagiwe n’uwuri muri uwu muriro hamwe n’uwuri hambavu yawo, kandi haninahazwa Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  27,9,Ewe Mussa (iii) mu vy’ukuri ni jewe Mana yawe mfise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi bukwiye
  27,10,"Nujugunye iyo nkoni yawe, mugihe yayibona igenda genda nk’inzoka yarahindukiye asubira inyuma yiruka atarindiriye, ewe Mussa (iii) ntutinye ntankeka iwanje ntibatinya imbere yanje intumwa z’Imana"
  27,11,"Mugabo uwahemukiye umutima wiwe hanyuma agaca akabisha ineza amaze kugira amabi, mbega jewe sije mfise ikigongwe n’Impuhwe zihagije"
  27,12,"Niwinjize ukuboko kwawe mumpuzu yawe, kuzoca gusohoka gufise ibara ryera atamwanda uriko, bikaba ari mubimenyetso icenda vyo kwa Fir’auni hamwe n’abantu biwe, mu vy’ukuri bari mubantu babi cane"
  27,13,"Mugihe bashikirwa n’ibimenyetso vyacu bigaragara, baciye bavuga bati:- ubu n’uburozi buri k’umugaragaro"
  27,14,Barayahakanye amajambo y’Imana matagatifu mugihe imitima yabo ivyemeza gutyo kubera ubuhemu bwabo n’ukwishima kwabo rero nuce uraba impera n’imperuka yabagira amabi
  27,15,"Ntankeka twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Suleimanu (iii) ubumenyi baca bavuga bati:- ininahazwa ryose ni ry’Imana yaduteye iteka ntangere gusumba benshi mubiremwa vyiwe vyamwemeye"
  27,16,"N’intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) niwe yatoranye ibisigi vy’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) nukuvuga iti:- mwebwe bantu mwe! Twebwe twarigishijwe imvugo z’inyoni nuguhabwa ibintu vyose, mu vy’ukuri iyi n’ingabirano y’Imana iri k’umugaragaro"
  27,17,Yaregeranirijwe Intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) ingabo ziwe z’ibisigo hamwe n’abantu n’inyoni nukuzitondesha imirwi n’iyindi
  27,18,"No mugihe bashika mumwaba w’ibikoko vy’ubunyegeri kimwe muri ivyo bikoko caravuze giti:- mwabunyegeri mwe! nimwinjire mumyobo yanyu intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) ntibahonyange n’ingabo ziwe mugihe itabumva"
  27,19,"Nawe aramweyura atwenga kw’ijambo ryiwe nuguca avuga ati:- ewe Muremyi wanje, numpe ubushobozi nce ndagukengurukira kumihezagiro wampaye jewe hamwe n’abavyeyi banje, kandi mbashe kugira ibikorwa vyiza ushima kandi unyinjize mumpuhwe zawe mbe mu bantu bawe beranda"
  27,20,"Hanyuma aragenzura zanyoni ziwe nukuvuga ati:- vyakabaye gute ko ntabona yanuma, canke yabaye muyitari ngaha"
  27,21,Mu vy’ukuri ndayihana ibihano bikaze cane canke ndayibage canke inzanire ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  27,22,"Nawe ntiyamaze igihe kirekire cane aca avuga ati:- ndatahuye ico utotahuye kandi nje nturuka mugihugu ca Saba’a ndakuzaniye inkuru y’imvaho"
  27,23,"Mu vy’ukuri sanze Umupfasoni ategeka kandi yahawe ibintu vyose, kandi akaba afise n’inyegamo y’iteka iteye igomwe niniya cane"
  27,24,"Ndamusanze ari kumwe n’abantu biwe bapfukamira izuba aho gupfukamira Imana yabo y’ukuri, Shetani nayo ikaba yarabasharijije ibikorwa vyayo hamwe nukubazitirira inzira yabo y’amahoro, kuri ivyo rero abo bantu bose ntibarongotse"
  27,25,Nimupfukamire Imana ikura ibintu vyinyegeje biri mumajuru no kw’Isi kandi ikaba ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza hamwe n’ivyo muserura
  27,26,Ntayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa Umuremyi w’inyegamo yiwe ntagatifu